des:
Amazon Alexa and the Eurom Smart products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. 

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 

After connecting Alexa to your Eurom Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Eurom Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Eurom Smart account in our "Eurom Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Eurom Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Eurom Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Eurom Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Eurom Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Eurom Smart", and you'll be navigated to Eurom Smart login page;
(9). Input your Eurom Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on light"
“Alexa, turn off light"
